SupplierPerformanceCriteriaSummary is a SummaryForm
    Layout
        display as text
            single column
                SupplierPerformanceCriteria.Criteria
                SupplierPerformanceCriteria.Description
                DerivedPerformanceRating
                    label is "Score"
                visible when (DisplayCommentsToSupplier)
                    Comments
                visible when (DisplayAttachmentToSupplier)
                    Attachment.File
                blank line
